OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FApart from the odd shower in
OL,6,Fthe north it will be a largely dry
OL,7,Fday. Variable amounts of cloud and
OL,8,Fsome bright or sunny spells. Colder
OL,9,Fthan yesterday.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA generally dry evening and
OL,12,Fnight although the odd shower possible
OL,13,Facross the north. Some clear periods
OL,14,Fovernight will lead to patchy frost.
OL,15,FLight winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FAfter a cold start the morning
OL,18,Fwill be dry and bright. Thickening
OL,19,Fcloud and outbreaks of rain will
OL,20,Fspread south later in the afternoon,
OL,21,Fclearing through the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
