OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry, bright and cold on Monday with a
OL,7,Ffew early showers. Sunny spells and a
OL,8,Ffew showers on Tuesday and Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
